OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FThree firms dominated      
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fforced meter installations 
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Three energy firms accounted for the   
OL,6, majority of forced prepayment meter    
OL,7, installations last year, the government
OL,8, has said.                              
OL,10,FBritish Gas, Scottish Power and Ovo    
OL,11,FEnergy made up 70% of all forced       
OL,12,Finstallations, government data shows.  
OL,14,FIn total, more than 94,000 prepayment  
OL,15,Fmeters were forcibly installed in 2022.
OL,17,FThe practice was halted after it       
OL,18,Femerged that debt agents acting for    
OL,19,FBritish Gas had broken into vulnerable 
OL,20,Fpeople's homes to force-fit meters.    
